    <div>Teaching Assistant, Instructor: Dr. Mohamad Ali Bijarchi</div>
  </li>
</ul>


<div class="mb-5 research-experiences-section" style="margin-top: 50px;">
  <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Research Experiences (RA)</div>
  <hr style="margin-top: 10px; border: 2px solid blue;">
